===簽證===
:參見：[[烏拉圭簽證政策|烏拉圭簽證政策]]和[[烏拉圭公民簽證要求|烏拉圭公民簽證要求]]
:以及：[[越南簽證政策|越南簽證政策]]和[[越南公民簽證要求|越南公民簽證要求]]
兩國公民皆須申請[[簽證|簽證]]方可入境對方國家。自2017年起，持有[[烏拉圭護照|烏拉圭護照]]的烏拉圭公民可以申請30天单次入境电子签证，签证费为25美元。若只前往[[富国岛|富国岛]]，可在岛上免签证停留30天。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://discoverphuquoc.com/customsvisas.html#a4 |title=Phu Quoc Specific Decisions |accessdate=2014-03-28 |archive-date=2014-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223162312/http://discoverphuquoc.com/customsvisas.html#a4 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.vietseatourist.vn/News/category1/news-57/No-visa-required-for-tourists-to-Phu-Quoc-on-short-stay.html |title=No visa required for tourists to Phu Quoc on short stay |access-date=2014-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701095940/http://www.vietseatourist.vn/News/category1/news-57/No-visa-required-for-tourists-to-Phu-Quoc-on-short-stay.html |archive-date=2017-07-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.phuquocislandguide.com/phu-quoc-visa/#2015-vietnam-visa-updates|title=Phu Quoc visa policy|accessdate=|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2017-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171223042509/https://www.phuquocislandguide.com/phu-quoc-visa/#2015-vietnam-visa-updates|dead-url=no}}</ref>旅客必须从第三国直达富国岛或从河内机场或胡志明市机场办理完清关手续后前往国内航站楼办理手续。

持[[越南護照|越南護照]]的[[越南人口|越南公民]]必須申請簽證方可入境烏拉圭，但越南外交或公務護照持有人可以免簽證入境<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://lanhsuvietnam.gov.vn/Lists/BaiViet/B%C3%A0i%20vi%E1%BA%BFt/DispForm.aspx?List=dc7c7d75-6a32-4215-afeb-47d4bee70eee&ID=306 |title=EXEMPTION OF ENTRY VISA TO VIETNAM |accessdate=2014-03-28 |archive-date=2019-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190524191937/http://lanhsuvietnam.gov.vn/Lists/BaiViet/B%C3%A0i |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

